{"categories":["newsletter","travel-leisure"],"collections":"","description":"Explore the captivating allure of the \"Travel Guide Survey\" email template. This sleek design, swathed in a sophisticated black and dark theme, seamlessly fits into any travel or newsletter communication. Its one-column layout ensures an uncluttered, easy-to-read format, while the striking yellow elements act as guideposts, drawing the reader's eye to key information. The sans serif font used is modern, enhancing readability and user engagement. This template is perfect for conducting surveys, gathering valuable feedback from your travel community. It's an ideal blend of style and functionality, designed to entice your audience to participate and engage, thus strengthening your travel network. Experience the power of effective communication with this remarkable email template.","short_description":"Uncover the allure of our email template designed for travel surveys. Its sleek one-column layout, bold black and dark theme, accented with vibrant yellow, ensures readability. The modern sans serif font enhances user engagement. Ideal for collecting valuable feedback to strengthen your travel network.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Beefree_TemplateCatalog_ProfileImage_400x400_1.png","description":"A team of passionate designers, marketers, and technologists with an understanding that great design inspires action. At Beefree, we’re committed to creating responsive, mobile-friendly, and high-converting templates that empower teams to get more done with less time.","short_description":"","display_name":"Beefree Team","id":"beefree-team"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml